QuestData.Title: Baby Bird
QuestData.Description: <Ikky cheeps again, then begins gnawing on his foot.$B$BLooking out across the nearby hillside, you spy tiny ravager grubs inching along the grass.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather $1oa Ravager Grubs in the Shadowglade.
QuestData.CompletionText: <Ikky looks up at you, foot clamped in his beak, and lets out a muffled cheep.>
QuestData.RewardText: <You hold the handful of grubs out, steel yourself, and prepare to chew them up as a mama bird would.$B$BThankfully, Ikky snatches them from your hand before you can proceed.$B$BApparently kaliri don't do that.>
